supportDesc.extent: Part I: Folios 1-15. Part II: Folios 16-32. Part III: Folios 33-87. Part IV: Folios 88-93. Part V: Folios 94-99.;

layoutDesc.layout: Part I: 1 column(s); ruled lines: 20; written lines: 20; Catchowrds on every page. Some passages written in red ink. Part II: 1 column(s); ruled lines: 18-20; written lines: 18-20; Catchwords on every verso. Section titles given in larger characters. Part III: 1 column(s); ruled lines: 16-18; written lines: 16-18; Visible mastara ruling. Part IV: 1 column(s); ruled lines: 15; written lines: 15; Uniform layout. Part V: 1 column(s); ruled lines: 14; written lines: 14; Uniform layout. Visible mastara ruling.
